Hi!

I have download the newest PHPExcel 1.6.3 release

When replacing an old release with release 1.6.3 I get the following Debug Error:

..\PHPExcel\NamedRange.php line 187 - Call to undefined method PHPExcel::getNamedRange()

Any ideas to fix this problem?

Best regards, Elund
Sounds strange because that method still exists in 1.6.3. Maybe you forgot to copy the file PHPExcel.php when you updated?
Of course! Stupid me ;-) Thank you very much for your quick help :-)
